item.title: Please somoene teamview me or skype me .. hamza-dw
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

You must extract the files from the archive, you can download winrar or 7gzip to do that, you will then need to make sure you have the newest Java installed. If you have any errors while running the client then please post them here in the form of a picture, as for making you owner open your server and then go to the character folder once you log in, log out. Edit the newly created character file and edit the playerRights variable to 3, this is the owner rank.
